---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Plumber Cardinia Shire | Full Service Area | Pakenham &amp; Officer | (03) 9003 0108"
  canonical="https://pakenhamplumbers.com.au/cardinia-shire/"
  description="Licensed plumbers across the Cardinia Shire &mdash; Pakenham, Officer, Cardinia Lakes, Lakeside, Heritage Springs, Beaconsfield &amp; surrounds. 24/7 emergency, hot water, blocked drains, burst pipes, gas fitting. VBA-licensed, CoC on every job.">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Cardinia Shire &middot; full coverage</span>
      <h1>Plumbers across the <span class="accent">Cardinia Shire</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        From Officer in the west through Pakenham&rsquo;s estates to the semi-rural fringe,
        we cover the whole Cardinia Shire &mdash; one of Victoria&rsquo;s fastest-growing
        areas. Emergency, hot water, drains, burst pipes and licensed gas fitting, day or
        night.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Full coverage</span>
      <h2>Suburbs we cover.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Featured local-area pages.</h3>
        <p>Full local guides &mdash; the plumbing story for each estate and what we see most.</p>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <a class="area-pill" href="/cardinia-lakes/">Cardinia Lakes</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/lakeside/">Lakeside</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/heritage-springs/">Heritage Springs</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/officer/">Officer</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/beaconsfield/">Beaconsfield</a>
        </div>

        <h3>Other Cardinia Shire localities.</h3>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Pakenham (CBD)</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Pakenham East</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Pakenham Upper</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Nar Nar Goon</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Beaconsfield Upper</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Gembrook</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Maryknoll</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Tynong</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Bunyip</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Garfield</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Cockatoo</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Emerald</span>
        </div>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Two markets, one shire.</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Growth-corridor estates</strong> (Pakenham, Officer, Cardinia Lakes,
          Lakeside, Heritage Springs, Pakenham East): a constant flow of new-build fit-off,
          hot water and gas connections, plus the early-2000s estates now hitting the
          10&ndash;15 year hot-water replacement window and their first wave of tree-root
          drain blockages. Standard mains-connected, South East Water plumbing.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Semi-rural fringe</strong> (Beaconsfield, Pakenham Upper, Beaconsfield
          Upper, Gembrook, Maryknoll): larger and acreage blocks often running rainwater
          tanks, pumps and pressure systems alongside mains plumbing, and some on septic or
          on-site wastewater. We service the tank-and-pump side as well as the household
          plumbing.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Compliance, every job.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Plumbing:</strong> all work to AS/NZS 3500 (Plumbing &amp; Drainage), Victorian Plumbing Regulations 2018.</li>
          <li><strong>Gas:</strong> licensed gas fitting to AS/NZS 5601 with carbon-monoxide testing.</li>
          <li><strong>Certificate of Compliance:</strong> issued on every prescribed plumbing and gas job.</li>
          <li><strong>South East Water:</strong> connection and backflow-prevention requirements met.</li>
          <li><strong>Dial Before You Dig:</strong> checked before any excavation.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">All five services</span>
      <h2>What we do.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/emergency-plumber/"><h3>24/7 emergency plumber</h3><p>Burst pipes, sewer overflows, gas leaks, no hot water &mdash; day or night.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/blocked-drains/"><h3>Blocked drains</h3><p>CCTV, hydro-jet, root cutting and no-dig reline. From $180.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/hot-water-systems/"><h3>Hot water systems</h3><p>Same-day repair &amp; replace &mdash; gas, electric, heat-pump, solar.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/burst-leaking-pipes/"><h3>Burst &amp; leaking pipes</h3><p>Leak detection, repair &amp; relining. We isolate fast.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/gas-fitting/"><h3>Gas fitting &amp; leaks</h3><p>Licensed gas fitting, appliance install, CO testing, CoC.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Need a plumber anywhere in Cardinia Shire?</h2>
        <p>Estate or acreage, emergency or everyday. Licensed, insured, CoC on every job.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
